name: Lianna
coverLetter: I have a full time job at a hospital and just want to make some extra cash on the side to help pay my student bills off faster. I can help on weekends and part time evening hours during weekdays. I trimmed couple years ago for a friend back in college when we were growing. I do not recall how much we trimmed  but I can trim fast and love tasks where I can stay focused for long periods of time.
